Simple library for interacting with Apple's APNS servers.

The library is intended to be used in long running applications and has reconnect logic.

Support for the APNS Feedback service is also provided.

Follow this guide for setting up your APNS push certificates:
NOTE: Do not perform step 6
http://blog.serverdensity.com/2010/06/05/how-to-renew-your-apple-push-notification-push-ssl-certificate/

Use GoDoc to see usage documentation
